txt.en: For every difficult task you accomplished, servants of the Enemy sought to oppose it. But they were unable to succeed in these attempts, for always did you dare one more foray into Imlad Morgul, one more incursion to the Dead City.
Complete many quests in the reclamation of Minas Ithil.
